reviewText:
Campaign is great and looks like developers took insiration in first two dooms building it. This review is only for the campaign since I'm not playing multiplayer.

PROs:
- Graphics are amazing and well optimized. GTX980 produces stable 100+ FPS in 1080p.
- Action is fun, fast and challanging;
- Great variety of finishers and they don't break the pace of gameplay;
- Very satisfuing guns with mods;
- Monsters are great;
- Codex is interesting to read;
- Art is great (especially open areas and last levels).

MIXED:
- Ending is unsatisfying (I don't mean final boss)

